table_description: Information about a domain alias entry, including the parent domain, alias name, and verification status.

columns.name: kind
columns.description: The type or kind of the domain alias entry.

columns.name: parentDomainName
columns.description: The parent domain associated with the alias.

columns.name: domainAliasName
columns.description: The name of the domain alias.

columns.name: verified
columns.description: Indicates whether the domain alias has been verified.

columns.name: etag
columns.description: The etag identifier for the resource.

columns.name: creationTime
columns.description: The timestamp when the domain alias entry was created.
